{"tid":1000850,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下大家點定義咩叫自己人 咩叫外人？","createTime":"2019-01-29T16:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T17:54:51.000Z","uid":215046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"73bc5d6d4a39b458887b74ff85cf0a876c3774e1","tid":1000850,"uid":215046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:49:41.000Z","msg":"例如你個仔/女 有男女朋友<br />\n家庭聚會都有黎過 <br />\n中秋新年都會一齊食飯<br />\n你會唔會當佢自己人 <br />\n定係一日未結婚都算係外人<br />\n然後有啲咩唔想佢黎就話 <br />\n呀！ 我淨係預左<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自己人</span>黎<br />\n有無人做人男女朋友面對佢屋企人都有咁既情況"},{"pid":"05c9796135bb733b1168326a70a64539bacc1be7","tid":1000850,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:00:14.000Z","msg":"因為人哋個個都當你係外人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1685e1f9cbfcc2b28ffbde97db90de98730713","tid":1000850,"uid":215046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c9796135bb733b1168326a70a64539bacc1be7","tid":1000850,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:00:14.000Z","msg":"因為人哋個個都當你係外人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:01:02.000Z","msg":"好好笑"},{"pid":"4627542e5c718471fde22d5a1fbde69acc1edb1e","tid":1000850,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:54:51.000Z","msg":"咁去之前 叫你男朋友/女朋友 問清楚咪得<br />\n覺得個個case都唔同 <br />\n 姐係平時weekend 食飯預你<br />\n唔代表family trip要預你<br />\n但又唔代表團年飯 你唔去得<br />\n<br />\n佢句自己人 單純係解 冇預你 <br />\n但自己人 好聽啲 大家都有落枱階"}]}